description.en: Honeygain is a crowdsourced network company which enables other businesses to conduct web intelligence, market research and content delivery.
description.ga_IE: Is cuideachta líonra sluaite é Honeygain a chuireann ar chumas gnólachtaí eile faisnéis gréasáin, taighde margaidh agus seachadadh ábhair a dhéanamh.
